function series(obj, cname, n) {
  var rate = 0;
  var len = 0;
  for (var i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
    var r = run(obj, codec[cname]);
    rate += r[0];
    len += r[1];
  }
  rate /= n;
  len /= n;
  console.log(cname + ' ' + rate + '  ' + len);
  return [rate, len];
}

function forObj(obj) {
  var r = {
    JSON: series(obj, 'JSON', 20),
    msgpack: series(obj, 'msgpack', 20),
    bison: series(obj, 'bison', 20)
  };
  return r;
}
